data.description: Well maintained home on the upcoming Southeast side! Primary bedroom boasts a large bathroom with double vanity, garden tub and standing shower with a walk in closet. The  large kitchen hosts a breakfast bar that overlooks the living room and a walk in pantry, along with the gorgeous custom made barn doors enclosing the laundry closet. Beautiful wooden blinds stay. Welcome Home!  OPEN HOUSE SET 12/9 11A-2P & 12/10 1P-3P
